OK you have a file that consists of 48 parts:
f2k6x-dgr.001
to
f2k6x-dgr.048

Get WINRAR and select the first file right click it and select open with ...yep you got it winrar....drag the file out, it will or should be an ISO file place the ISO file on the desktop or a folder of your choice, then use nero or easy CD creator to burn the already XBOX "Chipped" compliant DVD.
